     <div type="preface">
   <pb facs="4"/>
   <head>The vvriting occasioning this Treatise.</head>
   <p>
      <seg rend="decorInit">I</seg> Desire to haue it proued, that the Religion now professed in <hi>England</hi> is the same which our Sauiour Christ taught his Apostles, and they preached ouer all they world, and conuerted thousands at one Sermon vnto.</p>
   <p>Jf it be the same, then there may bee some named that suffered for it: For it is not likely that so many thousands which were conuerted to the true Faith should all be destroyed, and no mention made of them in ancient Histories.</p>
</div>
